{"tid":1855583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[開始做神] 湖南衞監局局長過勞導致心肌梗塞亡","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T13:59:59.000Z","uid":64345,"like":214,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"08c15742f069bbbea45356060aaceede5f5a5844","tid":1855583,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:15:45.000Z","msg":"內地媒體報道，湖南衞生計生綜合監督局黨委書記兼局長張輝在今日凌晨逝世，終年56歲，他因過度勞累，導致突發心肌梗塞，搶救無效。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，自從新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情爆發以來，張輝一直在防控一線，先後帶隊到各大醫院發燒門診、車站碼頭、疾控中心、高速公路的路口、關卡等地，督導疫情防控措施落實。<br />\n<br />\n張輝於上月19至21日，帶隊到長沙及岳陽開展新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控專項督導，28至29日又帶隊到湖南的醫藥及消毒劑公司作衞生監督檢查。"},{"pid":"bcb137a642e43447fb00d095b72d047473e73d51","tid":1855583,"uid":262125,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:17:42.000Z","msg":"中肺炎？"},{"pid":"0a86176728362d45d5ad11644b7b72544ea59af2","tid":1855583,"uid":288707,"like":123,"dislike":3,"score":120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"讓領導先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e27310a5190e747f23bafdd1a8db6a20ede0d8","tid":1855583,"uid":103759,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"沒事～ 聽黨的話 跟黨走"},{"pid":"f6100d8959b1f77c8f740921177be5d216e5a48b","tid":1855583,"uid":199261,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"假新闻"},{"pid":"cf293ab86908b178a6a0a7c9aec74c9503dc61f3","tid":1855583,"uid":27250,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:19:30.000Z","msg":"馬上風"},{"pid":"5b16a081d85a982d613f6081ae747e9c9da0a280","tid":1855583,"uid":340106,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"黨會為你安排最好"},{"pid":"3547ba88d944e393f4bd298ca9caed11ad993e45","tid":1855583,"uid":19979,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"死亡筆記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"b61faacce